{"id":251,"parent_id":250,"book_id":95,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":251,"title":"Moroni 1","subtitle":"","short_title":"Moro.","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/1","content":[["div",[".title",["span.dominant","The Book of Moroni"]],[".titleNumber","Chapter 1"],[".studySummary",["i","Moroni writes for the benefit of the Lamanites—The Nephites who will not deny Christ are put to death. About",["span.small","A.D."],"401–421."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/1.1","order":"05.26.001.26087"},["b","1"],"Now I, Moroni, after having made an end of abridging the account of the people of Jared, I had supposed",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"not"],"to have written more, but I have not as yet perished; and I make not myself known to the Lamanites lest they should destroy me."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/1.2","order":"05.26.001.26088"},["b","2"],"For behold, their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"wars"],"are exceedingly fierce among themselves; and because of their",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"hatred"],"they",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"put to death"],"every Nephite that will not deny the Christ."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/1.3","order":"05.26.001.26089"},["b","3"],"And I, Moroni, will not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"deny"],"the Christ; wherefore, I wander whithersoever I can for the safety of mine own life."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/1.4","order":"05.26.001.26090"},["b","4"],"Wherefore, I write a few more things, contrary to that which I had supposed; for I had supposed not to have written any more; but I write a few more things, that perhaps they may be of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"worth"],"unto my brethren, the Lamanites, in some future day, according to the will of the Lord."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/1.1a","order":"05.26.001.26091"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/8.5"},"Morm. 8:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/10.1.1-2"},"Moro. 10:1 (1–2)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/1.2a","order":"05.26.001.26093"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/12.21.20-23"},"1 Ne. 12:21 (20–23)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/1.2b","order":"05.26.001.26095"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hate"},"TG Hate"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/1.2c","order":"05.26.001.26097"},["b","2c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/45.14"},"Alma 45:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/1.3a","order":"05.26.001.26099"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.33.32-33"},"Matt. 10:33 (32–33)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/29.5"},"3 Ne. 29:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/1.4a","order":"05.26.001.26101"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/3.12.11-12,19"},"2 Ne. 3:12 (11–12, 19)"],"."]]}
